      "title": "Major flood situation as water level of Kalu River tributary rises",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Department of Irrigation says that the water level of Kuda Ganga, a tributary of the Kalu River, has risen at Millakanda area to the level of a major flood situation.",
        "Meanwhile, the Department of Meteorology says that the low-level atmospheric disturbance around the island is gradually moving away."
      ],
